## Installation

Add the following dependency to your `pom.xml`:

```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>{{ sdk.gitUserName }}</groupId>
    <artifactId>{{ sdk.gitRepoName }}</artifactId>
    <version>{{ sdk.version }}</version>
</dependency>
```

